&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; What can I do to have such a facility through java code using JUnit.
&gt; 
&gt; How can I select which test to run ? even though I have read all
&gt; tutorials and practically conducted most of the tests successfully,
&gt; about this feature I am ignorant.

Create a TestSuite of only one test. You can choose the test to execute 
by setting the test&#39;s name:

public class SingleTest {
     public static Test suite() {
        TestSuite suite = new TestSuite();
        MyTestCase test = new MyTestCase();
        test.setName(&quot;testHello&quot;);
        suite.add(test);
     }
}

